{"tid":1932001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「自由搏擊」全民三罷定全民勇武？","createTime":"2020-03-18T12:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T15:48:10.000Z","uid":345458,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27e630cb295792ae9eb02032ae86c3c3fba6a748","tid":1932001,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post話準備全民勇武未笑咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1931865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1931865</a><br />\n<br />\n兩樣同時都係最直接可以令港共政權跪低嘅手段，同時亦都係令到香港人最易跪低嘅手段。<br />\n<br />\n全民三罷嘅指標，係最少二百萬人三罷，而且係<span style=\"color: red;\">無限期</span>。全民勇武嘅指標，係二百萬和理非變成勇武，而且係要<span style=\"color: red;\">衝到最前</span>嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一個冇咗條命，一個冇咗份工，大家點揀呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁梗係全民勇武啦，我寧願冇咗條命都要保住份工呀屌你！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁梗係全民三罷啦，我唔撚想死呀！"},{"pid":"9f5e0be74f84e939d5e7986ff1ad116c38d2f166","tid":1932001,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"兩樣都唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78085bbcf62f4cbf16c69a56b405eb80f4d197b2","tid":1932001,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"我先 冇咗份工你殺咗我算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1CrpK7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1CrpK7.jpg&h=8881f8a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7244a3792296ef080266cb8296acd2d437e5326","tid":1932001,"uid":159491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:47:14.000Z","msg":"一定要冇限期<br />\n有只會被人拉布<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2c79b71eaabd30789a5fbc0675464917f44442","tid":1932001,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"大人要返工，細路衝衝衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8872ace3734bef787d5297a96d72efec63b8c3b5","tid":1932001,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"點解要對立？<br />\n<br />\n200萬人罷工一定會勇武升級<br />\n唔會死因為夠多人<br />\n唔會炒因為夠多人"},{"pid":"24f55a8cafb810c1d2d8dd8b4e8c621ae2ffe5de","tid":1932001,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"how about鍵盤勇武？"},{"pid":"53a3fea6eea63f458bb1bff27e51625d52f00391","tid":1932001,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8872ace3734bef787d5297a96d72efec63b8c3b5","tid":1932001,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"點解要對立？<br />\n<br />\n200萬人罷工一定會勇武升級<br />\n唔會死因為夠多人<br />\n唔會炒因為夠多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"冇可能兩條一齊行<br />\n<br />\n你要知道搞三罷過程係好複雜<br />\n同埋就算你搞得成三罷<br />\n以香港人嘅唸法<br />\n邊有可能仲勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋「全民」呢兩隻字係重點"},{"pid":"303c41a0ffc6a95133911e61c36525998acdc480","tid":1932001,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24f55a8cafb810c1d2d8dd8b4e8c621ae2ffe5de","tid":1932001,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"how about鍵盤勇武？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為自己好幽默？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03859a8360e8cefeacb313327277df0c655c657e","tid":1932001,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8872ace3734bef787d5297a96d72efec63b8c3b5","tid":1932001,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"點解要對立？<br />\n<br />\n200萬人罷工一定會勇武升級<br />\n唔會死因為夠多人<br />\n唔會炒因為夠多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"唔會炒因為夠多人呢個我一直都buy嘅<br />\n但夠多人唔會死根本係呃埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5772e27517767ad0bb056cee768470185015fe","tid":1932001,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"其實兩樣野都無可能&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n晚清夠廢夠垃圾，黃花岡烈士都係唔夠一百人。<br />\n法國黃背心夠團結，一樣做唔到全民勇武<br />\n就連全民罷工都總有10%人永遠走去返工<br />\n視返工為信仰既香港就更絕望"},{"pid":"5aa820b4e51fd5424210c49a301f12766ff364cd","tid":1932001,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工係好大既先例"},{"pid":"605885924502131a04e3669a4164d77a628f721f","tid":1932001,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"有咩可能呀，個撚個攞住兄弟爬山呢句，乜嘢都諗住有人做，等天收等報應。<br />\n<br />\n仲想推手足出去死？ <br />\n<br />\n黎明行動大三罷個星期之後都知香港冇撚得救。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行動post唔撚做，罷工就影張相，&rdquo;雖然阻左我3個鐘，但#不割&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n跟住做埋啲on9贖罪嘢，叫你罷工就走去和你lunch<br />\n<br />\n成班所謂黃絲和理lunch，屌你老母叫你哋罷工你去做乜撚，放lunch出2個鐘企下，比狗圍又上網吹雞叫成班手足支援，之後班垃圾放完lunch就由我班手足係道頂，日撚日都拉一堆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢班自私既黃絲一日唔改變個心態，真係一日冇機會光復香港。<br />\n<br />\n唯一幾次所謂和勇合作咪機場接人同中大，成班uncle auntie真係出黎救人，而呢班和你lunch班所謂上班族咪繼續Instagram出post 好嬲好嬲。"}]}